{"title":"关于Hexo的介绍","uid":"b33ef4daf7376b2fb65f768223237990","slug":"图片文章","date":"2023-04-09T02:09:50.739Z","updated":"2023-04-09T10:06:29.706Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/图片文章.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://hexo-my.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/48540923dd54564e78ea6066bbde9c82d0584fe6.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"快速、简洁且高效的博客框架\"><a href=\"#快速、简洁且高效的博客框架\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\" 快速、简洁且高效的博客框架 \"></a><center> 快速、简洁且高效的博客框架 </center></h1><hr>\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-bottom: 75%;\"><iframe src=\"//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=39807850&cid=69927212&page=1\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"position: absolute; width: 100%; \nheight: 100%; left: 0; top: 0;\"> </iframe></div>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"Hexo剖析\"><a href=\"#Hexo剖析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Hexo剖析\"></a>Hexo剖析</h2><p>中文文档：<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/\">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/</a><br>官方主题库：<a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\">https://hexo.io/themes/</a><br>next主题：<a href=\"https://github.com/theme-next\">https://github.com/theme-next</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Hexo原理综述\"><a href=\"#Hexo原理综述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Hexo原理综述\"></a>Hexo原理综述</h2><p>markdown到html的旅程</p>\n<p>Hexo文件结构</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">├── _config.yml     <span class=\"token comment\"># 站点配置文件</span>\n├── db.json     <span class=\"token comment\"># database，缓存文件</span>\n├── node_modules  <span class=\"token comment\"># 安装的插件以及hexo所需的一些node.js模块</span>\n├── package.json  <span class=\"token comment\"># 应用程序信息，配置hexo运行需要的js包</span>\n├── public     <span class=\"token comment\"># deploy时生成，最终所见网页的所有内容</span>\n├── scaffolds  <span class=\"token comment\"># 模板文件夹，hexo默认包含以下三种布局(layout)    https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/writing.html</span>\n│     ├──draft.md   <span class=\"token comment\"># hexo new draft &lt;title> 会在source/_drafts目录下生成md文件</span>\n│     ├──page.md  <span class=\"token comment\"># hexo new page &lt;title> 在source目录下</span>\n│     └──post.md   <span class=\"token comment\"># hexo new post &lt;title>  在source/_posts目录下生成md文件</span>\n├── <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span>    <span class=\"token comment\"># 资源文件夹。除 posts 文件夹之外，开头命名为 (下划线)的文件 / 文件夹和隐藏的文件将会被忽略。Markdown 和 HTML 文件会被解析并放到 public 文件夹，而其他文件会被拷贝过去。</span>\n│     ├── _draft  <span class=\"token comment\"># 除 _posts 文件夹之外，开头命名为 _ (下划线)的文件 / 文件夹和隐藏的文件将会被忽略</span>\n│     └── _posts  <span class=\"token comment\">#</span>\n│             └──  hello-world.md\n└── themes   <span class=\"token comment\">#主题文件夹</span>\n      ├──\n      └──next\n          ├──\n          ├──\n          ├──\n          ├──\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>","feature":true,"text":" 快速、简洁且高效的博客框架 Hexo剖析中文文档：https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/官方主题库：https://hexo.io/themes/next主题：https://github.com/theme-next Hexo原理综述markdown到html...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":977,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E3%80%81%E7%AE%80%E6%B4%81%E4%B8%94%E9%AB%98%E6%95%88%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 快速、简洁且高效的博客框架 </span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Hexo%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Hexo剖析</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Hexo%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E7%BB%BC%E8%BF%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Hexo原理综述</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Johnny","slug":"johnny","avatar":"/medias/OIP-C.jpeg","link":"https://tridiamond.tech","description":"欢迎来到我的Blog","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/tridiamond","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Markdown语法","uid":"8577172d587822c13c6c2f341014a5ff","slug":"Markdown语法","date":"2023-04-09T07:49:36.000Z","updated":"2023-04-09T08:48:19.991Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Markdown语法.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cover.png","text":"Markdown语法详细介绍https://blog.51cto.com/u_14742462/3609101 ","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":56,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"测试","slug":"测试","count":2,"path":"api/categories/测试.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Markdown","slug":"Markdown","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Markdown.json"}],"author":{"name":"Johnny","slug":"johnny","avatar":"/medias/OIP-C.jpeg","link":"https://github.com/TriDiamond","description":"I am Johnny, how are you?","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Johnnyhhhhh","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},"next_post":{}}